@startuml
|User|
:Selects to view a specific project;

|System|
:Retrieves the project_id from the selection;
:Sends a query to fetch all employees associated with the project_id;

|Database|
:Returns the list of participants and their project-specific roles and metadata;

|System|
if(Did query returned any participant?)is(yes)then
    :Renders the "Project Participants" module within the UI;
else(no)
    |User|
    :Displays a message stating "No participants assigned to this project";
    stop
endif
:Views the display of participants;
stop

@enduml